{"tid":775651,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益-教曉阿媽反撃用個仔入到大學曬命既親戚","createTime":"2018-08-11T10:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T00:49:19.000Z","uid":175032,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e3052aac0e397ee3df59b0c220f8d2827d71a7","tid":775651,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"我有個舅母一向乜乜柒柒都鐘意同我屋企鬥<br />\n咁我表哥佢大仔當年入唔到大學(asso hd都冇）<br />\n我（下一年）我家姐（同年）兩個就入左Kong U <br />\n咁依幾年都已經成個怨婦咁單打我阿媽<br />\n一時又話家下大學生唔值錢<br />\n一時又話高分低能<br />\n到今年我個妹同佢細仔考dse<br />\n終於比佢光宗耀祖<br />\n恒大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個妹就失左手入左UST話要retake(no offense 但佢話我同家姐都Kong U所以佢都一定要入，我同家姐阿媽都有同佢講冇所謂）<br />\n問題黎喇<br />\n隻怨婦家下好似勝利者咁同我媽耀武揚威<br />\n平時都冇乜野<br />\n但今次我媽見到我妹唔開心已經好心疼<br />\n條友仲要串我個妹要retake<br />\n唔好話我假膠<br />\n我舅母真係低教育人士<br />\n真心唔知其實我個妹同佢個仔case係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我媽又唔係講野叻既人<br />\n有咩方法可以一兩句教識我媽反撃隻怨婦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adae3c35c0a98d99e758e43b04f11fe5460f1b3","tid":775651,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"同佢講屌你老母"},{"pid":"3e781d0e3af1ef18e04cbac61ebf837315748ce2","tid":775651,"uid":135445,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"恒大？<br />\n你個仔去踢波呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5c1094a95b82881ed05f0a968135bc8743e2fe","tid":775651,"uid":49979,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"高分低能同唔值錢真係聽過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係出自d仔女入唔到大學既親戚口中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到好似自己唔恨入咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係能力唔夠入唔到炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bcf3bf1c67993fde27d2fe3af6a22e9cedea68","tid":775651,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"斷關係唔好再見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c249656a9686f62e7340de8471dd872eccbba4","tid":775651,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bcf3bf1c67993fde27d2fe3af6a22e9cedea68","tid":775651,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"斷關係唔好再見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"我媽同佢細佬我舅父關係好好<br />\n我地表兄弟姊妹都會一齊玩<br />\n係舅母低低地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390de6008d0950a7a225f142f645e4fa9779f01f","tid":775651,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8c249656a9686f62e7340de8471dd872eccbba4","tid":775651,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bcf3bf1c67993fde27d2fe3af6a22e9cedea68","tid":775651,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"斷關係唔好再見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"我媽同佢細佬我舅父關係好好<br />\n我地表兄弟姊妹都會一齊玩<br />\n係舅母低低地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"你代老母串返佢囉<br />\n一係無視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9382a73ba4e603b2a6384e8c5b1b42642dfb1f7","tid":775651,"uid":97358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"KongU都唔識駁嘴<br />\n真係高分低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\